{"tid":1049017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英議會首舉行BNO平權會議 與會者倡重設居英權","createTime":"2019-03-06T03:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T07:04:38.000Z","uid":56881,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c84908836c48229225f6ab2f7ab570051e45a4","tid":1049017,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%A6%96%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8Cbno%E5%B9%B3%E6%AC%8A%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0-%E8%88%87%E6%9C%83%E8%80%85%E5%80%A1%E9%87%8D%E8%A8%AD%E5%B1%85%E8%8B%B1%E6%AC%8A-225819132.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258Cbno%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2580%25A1%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%25B1%2585%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%25AC%258A-225819132.html&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=ab7673d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%A6%96%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8Cbno%E5%B9%B3%E6%AC%8A%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0-%E8%88%87%E6%9C%83%E8%80%85%E5%80%A1%E9%87%8D%E8%A8%AD%E5%B1%85%E8%8B%B1%E6%AC%8A-225819132.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rNEkZdBqnbM_JyUHNkc6xA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/ca9bffb6299648588859640cc4ae02fb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrNEkZdBqnbM_JyUHNkc6xA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fca9bffb6299648588859640cc4ae02fb&h=8b525755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港截至2017年年底有逾15萬人持有BNO。<br />\n<br />\n2014年違法佔領行動後，有指港人對香港前途失去信心，掀起續領英國國民(海外)護照(BNO)風潮，香港截至2017年年底有逾15萬人持有BNO。英國議會於本周一(4日)首次舉行BNO平權會議，有持有BNO的港人專程參加。<br />\n<br />\n有與會者指，英國有意成為旅客電子通關的世界領導者，而美國、日本、南韓等地方旅客都可獲此優待，甚至香港特區護照持有人都可以使用快速電子通道，但令人不解的是BNO持有人卻沒有這待遇，促請英國允許BNO持有人可以使用快速電子通道入境英國。<br />\n<br />\n另外，亦有與會者指自佔領行動後，大批港人對前景失去希望，根據1948年英國國籍法，所有在港出生的香港公民都享有英國居留權，惟1962年英聯邦移民法案實施後，港人居英權被剝奪，故希望1961年2月4日前出生的香港公民，都有資格註冊為英國公民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要比一早比左<br />\n依家會肯比BNO有居英權咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c91d57425d48380367931bf54b6c9ff7110fde","tid":1049017,"uid":170255,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:04:38.000Z","msg":"英國佬又等錢洗，又一堆人排隊互打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}